{"tid":2064603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵涌婆媳湊B起爭執 雙雙尋死1人昏迷","createTime":"2020-06-15T02:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T03:40:23.000Z","uid":137088,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0379f1e05992b80aae5512e6ebb3a18dda0bcdf3","tid":2064603,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】葵涌邨發生婆媳糾紛，兩人雙雙企圖自殺，送院救治，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n現場是秋葵樓一單位，昨晚11時許，56歲姓林的婆婆疑因照顧一歲男孫問題，與姓曹30歲媳婦發生激烈爭執，期間婆婆疑情緒激動，服下止痛藥丸企圖自殺，媳婦則飲清潔劑企圖自殺。其家人發現於是報警。救護員到場將兩人送仁濟醫院治理，其中一人昏迷，經搶救後恢復知覺。<br />\n<br />\n警方將案件列作企圖自殺，事件沒有可疑。"},{"pid":"fb65ef954bd8c2c84aa6d48c5eacd5efe94a8fba","tid":2064603,"uid":34935,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"食止痛藥自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未聽過"},{"pid":"e8ad3e1534d4044a1636c31984f4a663fe1e3ac6","tid":2064603,"uid":54647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb65ef954bd8c2c84aa6d48c5eacd5efe94a8fba","tid":2064603,"uid":34935,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"食止痛藥自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未聽過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"你試下"},{"pid":"792e634dc85a076254ba460711691ed43abc4653","tid":2064603,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fb65ef954bd8c2c84aa6d48c5eacd5efe94a8fba","tid":2064603,"uid":34935,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:42:43.000Z","msg":"食止痛藥自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未聽過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"遍的撲息熱痛(Paracetamol)，屬第一線藥物<br />\n<br />\n這類藥物不用醫生處方也可買到。它具止痛及退燒功效，副作用少，相對較安全，但沒有消炎作用。其每日上限為4000mg。(如每粒500mg，即每天最多吃8粒)，每次不能超過1000mg(即約兩粒)，否則或會損害肝功能，嚴重者會令肝中毒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtynEO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtynEO1.jpg&h=2bcfee